title: Bryan P. Mayfield, PharmD, BCGP
text:
Data Scientist | Medical Writer | Board Certified Geriatric Pharmacist

I am currently a Research Data Scientist at Precision Analytical where I work on interesting things centered around menopause, hormones, and aging.
My passion lies at the intersection of data science, scientific communication, geriatrics, health disparities, pharmacoeconomics, pharmacoepidemiology, and health outcomes research.
